From: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>
Date: Sat, 24 Jan 2026 23:43:34 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] ASK: Add EtherIP and 4RD tunnel support for Layerscape

Port NXP ASK patches to iproute2 6.13.0:
- EtherIP over IPv6 tunnel support (ip/ip6tunnel.c)
- EtherIP over IPv4 tunnel support (ip/iptunnel.c)
- 4RD (IPv4 Rapid Deployment) tunnel support

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [NXP ASK extensions]
Signed-off-by: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>

